  fhir:DomainResource.text [
     fhir:Narrative.status [ fhir:value "extensions" ] ;
     fhir:Narrative.div "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Generated Narrative: ValueSet VarighedPostOPTrombDKR</b></p><a name=\"VarighedPostOPTrombDKR\"> </a><a name=\"hcVarighedPostOPTrombDKR\"> </a><p>This value set includes codes based on the following rules:</p><ul><li>Include these codes as defined in <a href=\"CodeSystem-Cyclus.html\"><code>https://kip.rkkp.dk/fhir/CodeSystem/Cyclus</code></a><span title=\"Version is not explicitly stated, which means it is fixed to the version provided in this specification\"> version ?2.23.1</span><table class=\"none\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b>Definition</b></td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-Cyclus.html#Cyclus-le5-dage\">le5-dage</a></td><td>&lt;= 5 dage (kun under indlæggelse)</td><td>&lt;=5 dage</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-Cyclus.html#Cyclus-6-10-dage\">6-10-dage</a></td><td>6-10 dage (forlænget profylakse)</td><td>6-10 dage</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-Cyclus.html#Cyclus-gt10-dage\">gt10-dage</a></td><td>&gt;10 dage (ekstra forlænget profylakse)</td><td>&gt;10 dage</td></tr></table></li><li>Include these codes as defined in <a href=\"CodeSystem-Medicine.html\"><code>https://kip.rkkp.dk/fhir/CodeSystem/Medicine</code></a><span title=\"Version is not explicitly stated, which means it is fixed to the version provided in this specification\"> version ?2.23.1</span><table class=\"none\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b>Definition</b></td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-Medicine.html#Medicine-beh-vitamin_k\">beh-vitamin_k</a></td><td>Patienten er i varig behandling med Vitamin-K-antagonist og fortsætter med tromboseprofylakse umiddelbart postoperativt indtil INR er i niveau</td><td>Behandling med vitamin-K-antagonist</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-Medicine.html#Medicine-noak_a\">noak_a</a></td><td>Patienten er i varig NOAK-behandling og fortsætter med vanligt præparat i halv dosering de første 1-2 postoperative døgn</td><td>NOAK halv dosis</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-Medicine.html#Medicine-noak_b\">noak_b</a></td><td>Patienten er i varig NOAK-behandling og fortsætter med vanligt præparat i fuld dosering umiddelbart (på operationsdagen)</td><td>NOAK fuld dosis</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-Medicine.html#Medicine-noak_c\">noak_c</a></td><td>Patienten er i varig NOAK-behandling og fortsætter med vanligt præparat i fuld dosering fra første postoperative dag</td><td>NOAK fuld dosis postop</td></tr></table></li><li>Include these codes as defined in <a href=\"CodeSystem-GenericValues.html\"><code>https://kip.rkkp.dk/fhir/CodeSystem/GenericValues</code></a><span title=\"Version is not explicitly stated, which means it is fixed to the version provided in this specification\"> version ?2.23.1</span><table class=\"none\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b>Definition</b></td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-GenericValues.html#GenericValues-other\">other</a></td><td>Andet</td><td>Other - used to choose unspecific value not in a valueset</td></tr></table></li></ul></div>"
  ] ;
